## ROADMAP updates

Update [ROADMAP.md](../ROADMAP.md) when:

- A phase gate passes → move to Completed with date
- Current phase changes → update Current section
- Blockers discovered → note in Current or Next

Do **not** put phase tables in AGENTS.md or CLAUDE.md.

### Phase gate example (Phase 1)

```markdown
## Completed
| Phase 1 | 2026-07-XX | Scaffold gate passed |

## Current phase: Phase 2 — Gateway + session + catalog
```

