## FAILURE-SCENARIOS matrix

[docs/FAILURE-SCENARIOS.md](../docs/FAILURE-SCENARIOS.md) holds the table; sequences hold the detail.

When adding a failure mode:
1. Add row to matrix (Detection, Action, Sequence link)
2. Create or update sequence file
3. Add test coverage note
4. Reference from saga code comments only if non-obvious

