## ADR process

Location: `docs/adr/ADR-NNN-short-title.md`

Create or finalize ADR when:
- Separate orchestrator repo (ADR-001) — done
- New integration pattern (events vs REST)
- Session storage change (Redis)
- Reconciliation strategy change

ADR template sections:
- Status (Proposed / Accepted / Superseded)
- Context
- Decision
- Consequences

Phase 1 carries stubs; finalize when implementing.

