## CLAUDE.md discipline

[CLAUDE.md](../CLAUDE.md) must stay **≤150 lines**.

Contains only:
- Mission (one paragraph + repo links)
- Commands (verify, pytest, compose)
- Read order
- Quality gates pointer
- Never do / Always do lists
- Module map one-liner
- Key doc links table

Move detailed content to ARCHITECTURE.md, ADRs, or cursor rules.

