## PR documentation checklist

From `.github/pull_request_template.md`:

```markdown
## Documentation
- [ ] AI-USAGE.md updated
- [ ] ROADMAP.md — if phase gate passed
- [ ] sequences/ + FAILURE-SCENARIOS — if flow changed
- [ ] PERFORMANCE.md — if timeout/retry changed
- [ ] ADR — if architectural
```

Agent must check applicable boxes honestly.

---

## Documentation anti-patterns

- Phase status in AGENTS.md (use ROADMAP)
- Monolithic sequence doc (use sequences/ directory)
- AI-DECLARATION.md in orchestrator
- Copying entire ADR into KB-IHMS
- Stale ROADMAP (update on gate pass)
- Empty AI-USAGE session log for AI-assisted PRs
- Embedding timeout values only in code — also PERFORMANCE.md

